Just like before.

34
00:02:51,990 --> 00:02:54,150
How can it be the same?

35
00:02:54,150 --> 00:02:59,710
My status is different now, so my mindset has to change too.

36
00:03:04,470 --> 00:03:06,075
Huan Er.

37
00:03:06,660 --> 00:03:10,370
When are we going to tell our parents about us?

38
