- I... 
 - Huan Er.

39
00:03:13,060 --> 00:03:15,620
- Huan Er. 
 - Uncle Chen.

40
00:03:15,620 --> 00:03:17,580
Xi Chi's here.

41
00:03:18,150 --> 00:03:21,470
It's so early. What are you two doing here?

42
00:03:22,375 --> 00:03:24,540
Well, school is about to start, isn't it?

43
00:03:24,540 --> 00:03:26,580
We're just discussing something.

44
00:03:26,580 --> 00:03:29,764
Yes. Dad, where's Mom? Is she still sleeping?

45
00:03:29,764 --> 00:03:32,500
Right. This time, pack more clothes when you go.

46
00:03:32,500 --> 00:03:34,750
And pack your toiletries separately from your clothes.

47
00:03:34,750 --> 00:03:36,520
Don't get it all over the place like last time.

48
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:39,710
Okay. I've packed them all.

49
