Xi Chi, it's been hard for you these past few days.

51
00:03:49,910 --> 00:03:52,270
No. This is what I should do.

52
00:03:52,270 --> 00:03:54,990
There's something else I'd like to ask you.

53
00:03:54,990 --> 00:03:56,030
Go ahead, Uncle.

54
00:03:56,030 --> 00:04:01,120
That is, when you go to school, please take care of Huan Er for me.

55
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:02,968
- No problem. 
 - I know there are

56
00:04:02,968 --> 00:04:08,030
many handsome guys and temptations at university.

57
00:04:08,030 --> 00:04:09,940
Keep a close eye on her.

58
00:04:09,940 --> 00:04:12,470
Don't let any boy trick my girl away.

59
00:04:12,470 --> 00:04:15,540
Dad, what are you saying?

60
00:04:15,540 --> 00:04:17,160
What? Did I say anything wrong?

61
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:19,581
Sure, no problem, Uncle. Don't worry.

62
00:04:19,581 --> 00:04:21,710
- I will take good care of Huan Er. 
 - Good.

63
00:04:21,710 --> 00:04:25,070
I'll leave her with you then.

64
00:04:26,200 --> 00:04:29,100
I'll make you two some breakfast. You can have a chat.

65
00:04:29,100 --> 00:04:30,620
Okay.

66
