No, right now I...

67
00:04:40,740 --> 00:04:44,980
With your dad saying that, I feel like the big bad wolf who steals what he's supposed to guard.

68
00:04:44,980 --> 00:04:46,940
What should we do?

69
00:04:47,780 --> 00:04:51,630
Maybe... maybe we shouldn't tell them yet, especially not my dad.

70
00:04:51,630 --> 00:04:56,200
He's probably not ready to accept our relationship right now.

71
00:04:58,100 --> 00:04:59,740
Okay.

72
00:05:00,320 --> 00:05:05,780
By the way, you haven't told Qi Qi and Song Cong about us, have you?

73
00:05:05,780 --> 00:05:07,420
I... They already know.

74
00:05:07,420 --> 00:05:09,950
- Since when? 
 - I told them last night.

75
00:05:09,950 --> 00:05:12,300
- Why didn't you tell me? 
 - My back hurts.

76
00:05:12,300 --> 00:05:15,540
 Xi Chi, do you eat milk and eggs? 

77
00:05:16,540 --> 00:05:19,040
I'm not eating, Uncle. I have something to do.

78
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:19,820
I'll go now. I'm not eating.

79
00:05:19,820 --> 00:05:22,630
- Have breakfast here. 
 - How do I dare to sit here and eat?

80
00:05:22,630 --> 00:05:24,520
Bye, Uncle.

81
00:05:27,950 --> 00:05:29,470
Thanks.

82
00:05:32,420 --> 00:05:34,120
Be careful. It's hot.

83
00:05:37,540 --> 00:05:39,300
Thank you.

84
00:05:40,642 --> 00:05:42,286
It's so good.

85
00:05:45,320 --> 00:05:47,630
You've got some on your lips. Wipe it off.

86
00:05:47,630 --> 00:05:50,150
Stop it. They're sitting here watching.

87
00:05:50,150 --> 00:05:52,150
What's wrong?

88
00:05:52,150 --> 00:05:53,760
I'll wipe it off myself.

89
00:05:53,760 --> 00:05:55,980
- They're watching us. 
 - What's wrong?

90
00:05:55,980 --> 00:05:57,180
They're calm.

91
00:05:57,180 --> 00:05:59,830
Like it's no big deal, they're not even surprised.

92
00:05:59,830 --> 00:06:02,100
We knew you two would be together.

93
00:06:02,100 --> 00:06:04,920
The whole world knew you liked each other.

94
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:06,950
Was it that obvious?

95
00:06:06,950 --> 00:06:08,070
How can it not be?

96
00:06:08,070 --> 00:06:10,597
You were practically orbiting around her every day.

97
00:06:11,220 --> 00:06:13,300
Huan Er, listen.

98
00:06:13,300 --> 00:06:15,520
Xi Chi has liked you for a while.

99
00:06:15,520 --> 00:06:18,420
He was afraid to confess, fearing you'd reject him.

100
00:06:18,420 --> 00:06:20,420
Really?

101
00:06:20,420 --> 00:06:21,950
Since when?

102
00:06:21,950 --> 00:06:25,050
- About since... 
 - Song&nbsp;Cong,

103
00:06:25,630 --> 00:06:28,980
can you stop broadcasting everything like a bullhorn?

104
00:06:28,980 --> 00:06:30,530
Okay.

105
00:06:31,231 --> 00:06:32,710
Since high school?

106
00:06:32,710 --> 00:06:34,300
- No, not that early. 
 - Since high school?

107
00:06:34,300 --> 00:06:38,130
Last Thursday night, around 8:40 p.m.

108
00:06:39,180 --> 00:06:41,630
We're still here. Stop showing affection.

109
00:06:41,630 --> 00:06:44,390
Are you going back to school tomorrow?

110
00:06:44,390 --> 00:06:45,831
Yes.

111
00:06:45,831 --> 00:06:46,853
What about you?

112
00:06:46,853 --> 00:06:49,160
We're going back tomorrow too.

113
00:06:49,160 --> 00:06:51,408
I've got to leave quickly. After I changed my major,

114
00:06:51,408 --> 00:06:53,200
my mom has been impatient with me every day.

115
00:06:53,200 --> 00:06:55,196
I can't stand it.

116
00:06:55,196 --> 00:06:57,220
Did you get the connecting tickets?

117
00:06:57,220 --> 00:06:58,950
Tickets are hard to come by now.

118
00:06:58,950 --> 00:07:01,510
We'll have to sit separately.

119
00:07:01,510 --> 00:07:03,050
No.

120
00:07:03,630 --> 00:07:06,950
Song Cong, which compartment did you get?

121
00:07:06,950 --> 00:07:08,760
Let me see.

122
00:07:11,950 --> 00:07:14,800
- Twelve. What about you? 
 - Twelve?

123
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:15,920
You bought a second-class seat?

124
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:17,360
Yes.

125
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:21,440
It's okay. They'd probably swap your second‑class seat

126
00:07:21,440 --> 00:07:22,710
for a business‑class one.

127
00:07:22,710 --> 00:07:24,860
I want to sit with you.

128
00:07:24,860 --> 00:07:26,540
Don't do that.

129
00:07:26,540 --> 00:07:29,200
We're just not on the road together.

130
00:07:29,200 --> 00:07:30,834
When we get there, I'll take you back to school.

131
00:07:30,834 --> 00:07:33,710
It's okay. It isn't worth much.

132
00:07:33,710 --> 00:07:35,490
It's decided.

133
00:07:43,630 --> 00:07:49,300
Qi Qi, didn't your mom freeze your card because you changed your major?

134
00:07:49,300 --> 00:07:51,100
I sold some of my old clothes and bags,

135
00:07:51,100 --> 00:07:53,108
- so I'm okay for now. 
 - Okay.

136
00:08:20,510 --> 00:08:23,808
I read the novel you posted online.

137
00:08:23,808 --> 00:08:26,253
