142
00:08:50,460 --> 00:08:52,700
I don't want to go abroad.

143
00:08:52,700 --> 00:08:57,440
You need more than talent to study literature. You need vision, insight,

144
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:59,631
experience and a strong philosophical foundation.

145
00:08:59,631 --> 00:09:02,440
No matter what direction you're going to take in the future,

146
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:07,320
