147
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:14,380
But writing for a living on a second-rate website only saps your passion for literature.

148
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:23,620
Are you afraid your boyfriend will stop you from going abroad?

149
00:09:25,780 --> 00:09:27,390
Listen here.

150
00:09:27,390 --> 00:09:32,210
Only incompetent men hinder their partner's growth.

151
00:09:36,650 --> 00:09:38,950
Think about it.

152
00:09:41,910 --> 00:09:47,810
Since you're going after your dreams, I want you to have no regrets.

153
00:10:05,230 --> 00:10:06,940
- Are you tired? 
 - No.

154
00:10:06,940 --> 00:10:09,560
This is nothing. Have you forgotten I have muscles?

155
00:10:09,560 --> 00:10:13,086
- I'm strong. 
 - Enough. All right.

156
00:10:15,910 --> 00:10:17,940
I've arrived. Give it to me.

157
00:10:17,940 --> 00:10:18,940
I'll walk you up.

158
00:10:18,940 --> 00:10:20,560
I'll go up myself.

159
00:10:20,560 --> 00:10:26,750
By the way, should we tell Zhou&nbsp;Ye and the others about us?

160
00:10:26,750 --> 00:10:30,350
Okay. I'll go back and find a chance to tell them.

161
00:10:30,350 --> 00:10:33,150
- Okay. 
 - Xi Chi, Huan Er.

162
00:10:33,150 --> 00:10:35,180
- Hui Xin. 
 - It's good you're all back.

163
00:10:35,180 --> 00:10:37,700
Call your roommates and have dinner in our dorm tonight.

164
00:10:37,700 --> 00:10:39,520
I've brought a lot of specialties from home.

165
00:10:39,520 --> 00:10:41,250
We'll make a hot pot together.

166
00:10:41,250 --> 00:10:44,780
Isn't it inconvenient for us girls to go to the boys' dormitory?

167
00:10:44,780 --> 00:10:46,030
Not really.

168
00:10:46,030 --> 00:10:47,720
Our dormitory isn't as strict as yours.

169
00:10:47,720 --> 00:10:49,000
Besides, it gets crowded at night.

170
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:52,700
When it's time, we guys will cover for you. You'll sneak in with the crowd.

171
00:10:53,390 --> 00:10:54,420
Come on, Huan Er.

172
00:10:54,420 --> 00:10:56,640
Or Hui Xin will be alone.

173
00:11:01,750 --> 00:11:06,030
All right. Worst‑case, we get a scolding. I'll go with Hui&nbsp;Xin.

174
00:11:06,030 --> 00:11:08,497
Hui Xin, see you this evening.

175
00:11:08,497 --> 00:11:09,750
Let's go back and tidy up.

176
00:11:09,750 --> 00:11:11,510
Okay. Let's meet this evening.

177
00:11:11,510 --> 00:11:15,230
Wait. You'd better tidy up. Don't leave smelly socks all over the place.

178
00:11:15,230 --> 00:11:18,508
How can that be? The boys' dorm is really clean, right, Zhou Ye?

179
00:11:18,508 --> 00:11:19,750
Clean? Is it clean?

180
00:11:19,750 --> 00:11:21,680
Of course it's clean. We'll get going now.

181
00:11:21,680 --> 00:11:22,810
Bye.

182
00:11:22,810 --> 00:11:24,360
- Bye, Huan Er. 
 - Bye.

183
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:26,280
Bye.

184
00:11:26,840 --> 00:11:28,542
- What's the hurry? 
 - Let's tidy up.

185
00:11:28,542 --> 00:11:30,875
Run quickly, and go back first.

186
00:11:41,820 --> 00:11:43,490
Oh, no.

187
00:11:44,230 --> 00:11:46,750
Wait, bro, why did you run so fast?

188
00:11:46,750 --> 00:11:48,909
Zhou&nbsp;Ye, put away the underwear on the balcony first.

189
00:11:48,909 --> 00:11:50,930
Yan&nbsp;Mu, wash your smelly socks.

190
00:11:50,930 --> 00:11:52,790
Now I'm going to fetch water and mop the floor.

191
00:11:52,790 --> 00:11:54,864
