192
00:11:54,864 --> 00:11:56,770
No, wait. Wait a minute.

193
00:11:56,770 --> 00:11:58,180
What are you doing?

194
00:11:58,180 --> 00:11:59,470
Are you role‑playing a dorm warden?

195
00:11:59,470 --> 00:12:02,229
