197
00:12:07,420 --> 00:12:11,600
Before the dormitory is cleaned, no one is allowed to leave.

198
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:14,300
No, Jing Xi Chi, you're being too much of an idol now.

199
00:12:14,300 --> 00:12:16,140
My girlfriend is coming and I said nothing about it. Why are you anxious?

200
00:12:16,140 --> 00:12:17,770
Just clean it up, okay?

201
00:12:17,770 --> 00:12:21,860
Or I won't help you with group work anymore.

202
00:12:24,780 --> 00:12:26,010
Wait, where is Zhang Yang?

203
00:12:26,010 --> 00:12:27,680
He's gone out to have fun.

204
00:12:27,680 --> 00:12:29,910
He...

205
00:12:33,910 --> 00:12:35,460
- Hi, Madam. 
 - You're back.

206
00:12:35,460 --> 00:12:37,210
Hi, Madam.

207
