Hi, Madam.

208
00:12:41,080 --> 00:12:42,530
You've gained weight.

209
00:12:42,530 --> 00:12:43,600
No.

210
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:45,200
Hi, Madam.

211
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:46,520
You're back.

212
00:12:46,520 --> 00:12:50,080
This is what you call a big crowd, and you think it's easy to sneak in?

213
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:51,600
I really didn't expect this.

214
00:12:51,600 --> 00:12:54,650
Aren't we being a little bold?

215
00:12:54,650 --> 00:12:56,130
Don't worry.

216
00:12:56,130 --> 00:12:59,600
With the way you three are dressed, who'd recognize you?

217
00:12:59,600 --> 00:13:01,650
Hello, Huan Er!

218
00:13:07,540 --> 00:13:08,530
Let's forget it.

219
00:13:08,530 --> 00:13:11,050
- I... 
 - No, Hui Xin. I've got it all ready.

220
00:13:11,050 --> 00:13:15,220
- I... 
 - Since we're here, let's go.

221
00:13:20,820 --> 00:13:23,230
Is this hairstyle for men or women?

222
00:13:23,230 --> 00:13:25,150
We can actually do this?

223
00:13:25,720 --> 00:13:27,643
Let's go. I'll cover you.

224
00:13:27,643 --> 00:13:30,142
Let's go. Hui Xin, it's going to be fine.

225
00:13:35,853 --> 00:13:38,110
Which dormitory are you from?

226
00:13:38,110 --> 00:13:41,320
Madam, it's me.

227
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:43,420
- Jing Xi Chi. 
 - Room 258.

228
00:13:43,420 --> 00:13:45,316
- Zhou Ye. 
 - Yes. Zhou Ye.

229
00:13:45,316 --> 00:13:48,042
- Which dormitory are they from? 
 - Madam, this is my junior, a street dancer.

230
00:13:48,042 --> 00:13:49,531
- Dance for her. 
 - Those weird clothes...

231
00:13:49,531 --> 00:13:50,650
Yeah. Look.

232
00:13:50,650 --> 00:13:53,708
Madam, you watch this TV series too?

233
00:13:53,708 --> 00:13:55,908
Let me tell you, my mom loves to watch this too.

234
00:13:55,908 --> 00:13:58,530
- Really? 
 - This guy's a scumbag.

235
00:13:58,530 --> 00:14:01,900
He ran off with his sister-in-law and cheated on his wife.

236
00:14:01,900 --> 00:14:04,050
- Which episode is that? 
 - All right, Madam. Enjoy it.

237
00:14:04,050 --> 00:14:05,440
I'll spare you the spoilers.

238
00:14:05,440 --> 00:14:08,810
- Does her husband divorce her? 
 - Yes.

239
00:14:08,810 --> 00:14:12,160
Catch me up on what's happened.

240
00:14:18,150 --> 00:14:19,080
Come on.

241
00:14:19,080 --> 00:14:22,080
The boys' dormitory is cleaner than the girls'.

242
00:14:22,080 --> 00:14:23,650
How can it not be?

243
00:14:23,650 --> 00:14:25,220
He made us clean it all afternoon.

244
00:14:25,220 --> 00:14:26,680
It's as if your girlfriend is coming over.

245
00:14:26,680 --> 00:14:28,442
Stop it.

246
00:14:29,200 --> 00:14:31,900
Wait, aren't we two chairs short?

247
00:14:31,900 --> 00:14:33,050
Oh, right.

248
00:14:33,050 --> 00:14:35,960
Yan Mu, go borrow two from the next dormitory.

249
00:14:35,960 --> 00:14:37,650
- No problem. 
 - Thank you.

250
00:14:37,650 --> 00:14:39,440
Come on, let's sit down. Sit down.

251
00:14:39,440 --> 00:14:41,650
- I'll help you. 
 - No. I can do it.

252
00:14:41,650 --> 00:14:43,660
I can do it.

253
00:14:45,820 --> 00:14:49,600
You still haven't told them we're dating?

254
00:14:49,600 --> 00:14:51,770
I just... haven't found the right time.

