522
00:34:08,742 --> 00:34:10,980
- Come back. 
 - We haven't seen enough.

523
00:34:10,980 --> 00:34:12,620
That's it?

524
00:34:18,670 --> 00:34:21,342
Qi Qi, what've you been up to?

525
00:34:21,342 --> 00:34:22,400
I haven't seen you around.

526
00:34:22,400 --> 00:34:24,620
I'm busy writing a novel.

527
00:34:24,620 --> 00:34:25,790
I changed my major.

528
00:34:25,790 --> 00:34:28,386
When my mom found out, she got so mad she froze my card.

529
00:34:28,386 --> 00:34:29,960
I have to make money.

530
00:34:29,960 --> 00:34:31,438
