531
00:34:31,438 --> 00:34:32,940
How much money do you make writing novels?

532
00:34:32,940 --> 00:34:35,146
I've got some money for drinks.

533
00:34:35,146 --> 00:34:38,080
Where is your boyfriend? Doesn't he care about you?

534
00:34:38,080 --> 00:34:41,060
It doesn't concern him. I don't want to bother him.

535
00:34:41,060 --> 00:34:45,920
Qi Qi, to be honest, are you happy in this relationship?

536
00:34:48,020 --> 00:34:49,710
I'm happy.

537
00:34:49,710 --> 00:34:51,560
Why do you ask?

538
00:34:53,240 --> 00:34:56,902
I just have a feeling you two aren't from the same world.

539
00:34:56,902 --> 00:34:58,346
Okay, I'll stop talking.

540
00:34:58,346 --> 00:35:00,246
Let's drink.

541
00:35:01,900 --> 00:35:04,750
Qi Qi, we're here.

542
00:35:13,920 --> 00:35:16,310
Song Cong, we're here.

543
00:35:18,226 --> 00:35:20,506
Song Cong?

544
00:35:21,620 --> 00:35:23,440
- Hi. 
 - Hi.

545
00:35:23,440 --> 00:35:25,620
How are you feeling?

546
00:35:26,350 --> 00:35:31,620
Am I drunk, or am I hallucinating?

547
00:35:31,620 --> 00:35:34,020
Xu Wen Wen called me and said you were drunk.

548
00:35:34,020 --> 00:35:37,140
She lied to you. I'm not drunk.

549
00:35:37,140 --> 00:35:40,080
She's just testing to see if you care about me.

550
00:35:40,080 --> 00:35:42,190
- What are you doing? 
 - Let's go back.

551
00:35:42,190 --> 00:35:43,720
I don't want to go back yet.

552
00:35:43,720 --> 00:35:45,940
Have a drink with me.

553
00:35:45,940 --> 00:35:47,830
You know I can't drink.

554
00:35:47,830 --> 00:35:49,290
Just a bottle.

555
00:35:49,920 --> 00:35:52,236
I have an exam tomorrow morning.

556
00:35:52,236 --> 00:35:54,197
One bottle.

557
00:35:59,500 --> 00:36:01,020
Okay. I'll have a glass of something with you.

558
00:36:01,020 --> 00:36:02,388
We'll leave after that, okay?

559
00:36:02,388 --> 00:36:03,990
Okay.

560
00:36:14,140 --> 00:36:16,140
- Let's go. 
 - No.

561
00:36:16,140 --> 00:36:17,790
Song Cong, what are you doing?

562
00:36:17,790 --> 00:36:20,910
Cheers. Let's drink!

563
00:36:25,710 --> 00:36:27,980
I'm dead drunk.

564
00:36:27,980 --> 00:36:29,720
You're fine.

565
00:36:30,831 --> 00:36:32,710
Come on, let's keep drinking.

566
00:36:32,710 --> 00:36:33,886
Stop it.

567
00:36:33,886 --> 00:36:34,960
Don't drink too much.

568
00:36:34,960 --> 00:36:37,770
I came here to drink and have a good time.

569
00:36:37,770 --> 00:36:42,590
If you don't let me drink... Don't kill the vibe.

570
00:37:11,940 --> 00:37:13,280
Xu Wen Wen.

571
00:37:13,280 --> 00:37:14,980
Let's drink.

572
00:37:15,880 --> 00:37:17,400
Song Cong, let's drink.

573
00:37:17,400 --> 00:37:19,468
Stop it.

574
00:37:19,468 --> 00:37:21,150
Come on.

575
00:37:24,100 --> 00:37:25,710
I told you not to drink so much.

576
00:37:25,710 --> 00:37:27,910
I just want to drink.

577
00:37:33,400 --> 00:37:34,620
How are you feeling?

578
00:37:34,620 --> 00:37:36,100
Are you okay?

579
00:37:36,100 --> 00:37:38,070
I'm fine.

580
00:37:39,730 --> 00:37:43,260
Song Cong, I want some water.

581
00:37:45,600 --> 00:37:47,060
I have an exam early tomorrow morning.

582
00:37:47,060 --> 00:37:49,820
When you're asleep, I'll go back.

583
00:37:50,620 --> 00:37:53,540
Are you leaving?

584
00:37:53,540 --> 00:37:56,230
Can you not go?

585
00:37:56,230 --> 00:37:58,790
I can't. I've got things to do in the morning.

586
00:37:58,790 --> 00:38:01,570
Why can't you stay with me?

587
00:38:05,080 --> 00:38:07,140
Song Cong,

588
00:38:07,830 --> 00:38:11,140
do you really like me?

589
00:38:11,140 --> 00:38:13,620
Of course I do.

590
00:38:13,620 --> 00:38:15,420
No.

591
00:38:15,420 --> 00:38:19,790
That's not how you like someone at all.

592
00:38:19,790 --> 00:38:23,360
You treat me totally differently than you treat Chen Huan Er.

593
00:38:23,360 --> 00:38:25,420
What does this have to do with Chen Huan Er?

594
00:38:25,420 --> 00:38:29,190
I've seen how you looked at her when you liked her.

595
00:38:29,190 --> 00:38:32,160
Wasn't that over ages ago?

596
00:38:35,090 --> 00:38:36,170
Yes.

597
00:38:36,170 --> 00:38:38,190
I liked Chen Huan Er before.

598
00:38:38,190 --> 00:38:41,320
But I also lost myself because I liked her.

599
00:38:41,320 --> 00:38:43,310
Now I don't think that's the right way to go.

600
00:38:43,310 --> 00:38:47,020
Is it wrong for me to like someone in a different way?

601
00:38:47,020 --> 00:38:49,230
Isn't it true that people grow up?

602
00:38:49,230 --> 00:38:51,890
Why are you so mean to me?

603
00:38:52,940 --> 00:38:56,230
So now you think I'm being unreasonable?

604
00:38:56,870 --> 00:38:59,500
I'm not being mean to you.

605
00:39:04,390 --> 00:39:10,980
I've been doing my best to be good to you, to be worthy of your love.

606
00:39:10,980 --> 00:39:14,620
But now you're telling me that's wrong too.

607
00:39:14,620 --> 00:39:17,453
So what should I do to be right?

608
00:39:18,420 --> 00:39:19,850
Okay.

609
00:39:20,420 --> 00:39:25,020
You said you shouldn't change yourself if you like someone.

610
00:39:25,020 --> 00:39:29,720
