611
00:39:31,230 --> 00:39:36,710
Over the past year, I've been acting the way you like in front of you.

612
00:39:36,710 --> 00:39:40,930
I've never been my true self in front of you.

613
00:39:44,270 --> 00:39:45,500
Don't you realize that?

