00:40:06,100 --> 00:40:09,790
I'll tell you what the real me is.

619
00:40:09,790 --> 00:40:12,120
The real me...

620
00:40:13,460 --> 00:40:17,547
The real me is the one who claims to be into literature,

621
00:40:17,547 --> 00:40:20,190
but in reality, I'm on a second-rate fiction site

622
00:40:20,190 --> 00:40:23,890
and I'm just spouting nonsense for the rewards.

623
00:40:23,890 --> 00:40:28,620
The real me is the one who says I have to rely on myself and not on my family,

624
00:40:28,620 --> 00:40:35,080
