625
00:40:35,750 --> 00:40:40,840
The real me obviously wants an equal love,

626
00:40:40,840 --> 00:40:46,780
but in an unequal relationship, I tread carefully,

627
00:40:46,780 --> 00:40:49,300
and lose myself.

628
00:40:55,710 --> 00:41:02,910
Do you still like this vain, weak...

629
