real me?

630
00:41:15,190 --> 00:41:17,670
Qi Qi, you're not like that.

631
00:41:17,670 --> 00:41:23,730
The girl I know is sensitive, but she’s kind, brave, and longs for freedom.

632
00:41:23,730 --> 00:41:30,330
You've always been Qi Qi. Dream-chasing, freedom-loving, and brave.

633
00:41:33,620 --> 00:41:36,460
But we all have to grow up.

634
00:41:37,060 --> 00:41:39,590
Isn't that what you said?

635
00:41:44,620 --> 00:41:46,790
Leave now.

